name: Stack

values.name: pop
values.comment: Removes the item at the top of the stack and returns it as the first item of a tuple.
values.type: Stack.Stack a -> ( Maybe.Maybe a, Stack.Stack a )

values.name: push
values.comment: Pushes an item onto the stack and returns the new stack. The item must be of the same type as the stack.

values.name: toList
values.comment: Convert a Stack type to a list data type

values.name: top
values.comment: Returns the top element of the stack without removing it.
